<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Medh Learning Platform</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #4a86e8;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-top: none;
        border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
      }
      .credentials {
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 15px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #4a86e8;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4a86e8;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Medh Learning Platform</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Welcome, {{name}}!</h2>
        <p>Thank you for registering with Medh Learning Platform. We're excited
          to have you join our community of learners!</p>

        {{#if password}}
          <div class="credentials">
            <h3>Your Login Credentials</h3>
            <p><strong>Username:</strong> {{email}}</p>
            <p><strong>Password:</strong> {{password}}</p>
            <p><strong>Note:</strong>
              Please change your password after your first login for security
              reasons.</p>
          </div>
        {{/if}}

        <p>With our platform, you can:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access a wide range of educational resources</li>
          <li>Track your progress and achievements</li>
          <li>Connect with peers and instructors</li>
          <li>Participate in interactive learning activities</li>
        </ul>

        {{#if loginUrl}}
          <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Login to Your Account</a>
          </div>
        {{/if}}

        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate
          to contact our support team.</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br />The Medh Learning Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy;
          {{currentYear}}
          Medh Learning Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>If you did not register for an account, please contact us
          immediately.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>